\end{align}

Assuming that $v/c \ll 1$, the beat frequency is:

\begin{equation}
\Delta \nu = 2\nu \frac{v}{c} \quad \text{(beat frequency)}
\end{equation}

For a receding car, proceeding along similar lines, the change in frequency is:

\begin{equation}
